  # How to Configure SEO in Next.js 16 (the Right Way)
  
  ### A Complete Guide to Metadata, Sitemaps, Robots, Structured Data & Social Sharing in the App Router
  
  [![JavaScript Development Space's avatar](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eFnX!,w_36,h_36,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F716a49f7-1d20-4a92-a255-d947c65e2995_512x512.png)](https://substack.com/@jsdevspace)
  
